elements.name: Payment online for Registration for Farmers’ Cooperative Association, Society or Company

steps.name: I am on SFWF Front Office Home Page "Chrome"
I Input Registered User's Username "Suraj" and Password "Admin@123"
I Click on Sign In button
I Verify Applicant's Successful Login
I Click on Register as Farmer
I Verify that User is directed to My Application Page
I Verify display of Farmers Card link
I Verify Programmes link
I Click on New Button to apply for Registration
I Verify display of Registration Type Page
I Click on Farmers Cooperatives Association, Society or Company
I Verify display of Registration of Farmers page
I Input Associate/Society/Company Name "ABC Agro Co Ltd"
I Input Represented by "Mr John Brown"
I Input Business Registration No.(BRN) "C123456789"
I Input Certificate of Incorporation No "XLPR852"
I Select Activity "Full Time"
I Input Office Phone Number "2126666"
I Input Mobile Phone Number "58967896"
I Input Office Address "The Main Road, Grand Port"
I Select Status of Applicant "Company"
I Select Duration Year for Registration membership "1"
I Input List of Products manufactured "Tomato, Pepper"
I Input No. of persons employed "50"
I Input Actual Annual Turnover (Rs) "10000000"
I Select Status of business "Existing"
I Input No. of years of operation "5"
I Click on Save and Continue
I Verify Upload Required Documents Page is displayed
I Upload Business Registration Card "src\test\resources\Upload_Test1.pdf"
I Upload Certificate of Incorporation "src\test\resources\Upload_Test1.pdf"
I Upload List of Directors/ Associates "src\test\resources\Upload_Test1.pdf"
I Upload Board Resolution of Enterprise for appointment of representative(s) "src\test\resources\Upload_Test1.pdf"
I Upload National Identity card of representative "src\test\resources\Upload_Test1.pdf"
I Upload Location Plan Document "src\test\resources\Upload_Test1.pdf"
I Upload Copy of SMEDA Certificate Document "src\test\resources\Upload_Test1.pdf"
I Upload Copy of Utility Bill Document "src\test\resources\Upload_Test1.pdf"
I Verify for Document Upload Success Message
I Click on Add Additional Document
I Input Additional Document Name "Additional Document Test"
I Verify Success message for adding Additional Document Name
I Upload Additional Documents "src\test\resources\Upload_Test1.pdf"
I Verify for Document Upload Success Message
I Click on Save and Continue
I Verify Terms and Conditions Page
I click on I agree to the Terms and Conditions
I Select Bank "ABC Banking"
I Input Bank Branch "Port Louis"
I Input Personal Bank Account Number"0001252563636"
I Click on Submit Application "Yes"
I Verify Success message for application submitted
I Verify Application Status "Submitted"
I Verify Payment Status "Pending"
I Copy Application Number
I Click on Shopping Cart for payment
I Select Application for payment
I Click on Proceed to Payment
I Click on Payment Icon
I Select Payment Method "Credit"
I Click on Final Proceed to Online Payment
I Verify display of Payment Gateway
